ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1849]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hirata Tōsuke|ja|平田東助|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a bureaucrat and politician (died [[1925]]). * 嘉永4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1851]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ogino Ginko|ja|荻野吟子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a feminist and Japan’s first female doctor (died [[1913]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1855]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sugiura Shigetake|ja|杉浦重剛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a thinker and educator (died [[1924]]). * 安政6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1859]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yasui Rimin|ja|安井理民|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, founder of the first Sōbu Railway (died [[1894]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1872]] {{ill|April 10|ja|4月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Itay