* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1642]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|徳川幕府|qq=|12=draft}} established the office of {{ill|Kanjō Bugyō|ja|勘定奉行|qq=|12=draft}}.
