{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=三月初七|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 3월 7일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 7''' is the 7th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1583]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|羽柴秀吉|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} (later known as {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) caused the fall of {{ill|Kashida Katsuie|ja|柴田勝家|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}’s forces by capturing the castle at {{ill|Ise Province|ja|伊勢|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}’s {{ill|Kameyama Castle (Ise Province)|ja|亀山城 (伊勢国)|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} in a prelude to the {{ill|Battle of Shizugatake|ja|賤ヶ岳の戦い|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1603]] {{ill|April 14|ja|4月14日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Nihonbashi|ja|日本橋|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} in Chūō, Tokyo, was opened. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1642]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|徳川幕府|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} established the office of {{ill|Kanjō Bugyō|ja|勘定奉行|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1854]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate and U.S. envoy Perry signed the {{ill|Nippon-America Treaty|ja|日米和親条約|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} (Kanagawa Treaty) in Yokohama, ending Japan’s national seclusion. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1860]] {{ill|March 24|ja|3月24日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – During the [[Sakuradamon Incident|桜田門外の変]], Tairō {{ill|Ii Naosuke|ja|井伊直弼|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} was attacked and killed by rōnin outside Sakurada Gate of Edo Castle. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Higashiyama Road Vanguard Government executed officials, including members of the {{ill|Akahōtai|ja|赤報隊|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, as pseudo-officials.
== Births == * [[Shōō (Kamakura period)|Shōō]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1288]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Later Fushimi Tennō|ja|後伏見天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 93rd {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1336]]). * [[Tenbun]] 18th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1549]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tsuchi no Junkei|ja|筒井順慶|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Sengoku daimyō (died [[1584]]). * {{ill|Kannen|ja|寛延|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1749]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ōta Nan-Ō|ja|大田南畝|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a playwright (died [[1823]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1825]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shiranui Kōuenemon|ja|不知火光右ヱ門|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 11th Yokozuna (died [[1879]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1832]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Matsunomon Sansōko|ja|松の門三艸子|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a waka poet and geisha (died [[1914]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1849]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hirata Tōsuke|ja|平田東助|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a bureaucrat and politician (died [[1925]]). * 嘉永4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1851]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ogino Ginko|ja|荻野吟子|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a feminist and Japan’s first female doctor (died [[1913]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1855]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sugiura Shigetake|ja|杉浦重剛|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a thinker and educator (died [[1924]]). * 安政6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1859]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yasui Rimin|ja|安井理民|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, founder of the first Sōbu Railway (died [[1894]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1872]] {{ill|April 10|ja|4月10日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Itaya Hazan|ja|板谷波山|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a ceramic artist (died [[1963]]).
