{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=三月初七|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 3월 7일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 7''' is the 7th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senbu|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1583]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 24|qq=}}) – {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|羽柴秀吉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=}} (later known as {{ill|Toyotomi Hideyoshi|ja|豊臣秀吉|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Toyotomi Hideyoshi|qq=}}) caused the fall of {{ill|Kashida Katsuie|ja|柴田勝家|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kashida Katsuie|qq=}}’s forces by capturing the castle at {{ill|Ise Province|ja|伊勢|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ise Province|qq=}}’s {{ill|Kameyama Castle (Ise Province)|ja|亀山城 (伊勢国)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kameyama Castle (Ise Province)|qq=}} in a prelude to the {{ill|Battle of Shizugatake|ja|賤ヶ岳の戦い|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Battle of Shizugatake|qq=}}. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1603]] {{ill|April 14|ja|4月14日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 14|qq=}}) – {{ill|Nihonbashi|ja|日本橋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nihonbashi|qq=}} in Chūō, Tokyo, was opened. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 19th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1642]] {{ill|April 2|ja|4月2日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 2|qq=}}) – The {{ill|Tokugawa shogunate|ja|徳川幕府|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa shogunate|qq=}} established the office of {{ill|Kanjō Bugyō|ja|勘定奉行|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanjō Bugyō|qq=}}. * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1854]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 31|qq=}}) – The Tokugawa shogunate and U.S. envoy Perry signed the {{ill|Nippon-America Treaty|ja|日米和親条約|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nippon-America Treaty|qq=}} (Kanagawa Treaty) in Yokohama, ending Japan’s national seclusion. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1860]] {{ill|March 24|ja|3月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 24|qq=}}) – During the [[Sakuradamon Incident|桜田門外の変]], Tairō {{ill|Ii Naosuke|ja|井伊直弼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naosuke|qq=}} was attacked and killed by rōnin outside Sakurada Gate of Edo Castle. * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keiō|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1868]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 26|qq=}}) – The Higashiyama Road Vanguard Government executed officials, including members of the {{ill|Akahōtai|ja|赤報隊|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Akahōtai|qq=}}, as pseudo-officials.
== Births == * [[Shōō (Kamakura period)|Shōō]] 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1288]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Later Fushimi Tennō|ja|後伏見天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Later Fushimi Tennō|qq=}}, the 93rd {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor of Japan|qq=}} (died [[1336]]). * [[Tenbun]] 18th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1549]] {{ill|March 31|ja|3月31日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 31|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tsuchi no Junkei|ja|筒井順慶|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchi no Junkei|qq=}}, a Sengoku daimyō (died [[1584]]). * {{ill|Kannen|ja|寛延|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannen|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1749]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 19|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ōta Nan-Ō|ja|大田南畝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōta Nan-Ō|qq=}}, a playwright (died [[1823]]). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunsei|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1825]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 20|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shiranui Kōuenemon|ja|不知火光右ヱ門|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiranui Kōuenemon|qq=}}, the 11th Yokozuna (died [[1879]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1832]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 3|qq=}}) – {{ill|Matsunomon Sansōko|ja|松の門三艸子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Matsunomon Sansōko|qq=}}, a waka poet and geisha (died [[1914]]). * {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1849]] {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 26|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hirata Tōsuke|ja|平田東助|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hirata Tōsuke|qq=}}, a bureaucrat and politician (died [[1925]]). * 嘉永4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1851]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 4|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ogino Ginko|ja|荻野吟子|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ogino Ginko|qq=}}, a feminist and Japan’s first female doctor (died [[1913]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1855]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 19|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sugiura Shigetake|ja|杉浦重剛|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sugiura Shigetake|qq=}}, a thinker and educator (died [[1924]]). * 安政6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1859]] {{ill|April 5|ja|4月5日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 5|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yasui Rimin|ja|安井理民|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasui Rimin|qq=}}, founder of the first Sōbu Railway (died [[1894]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1872]] {{ill|April 10|ja|4月10日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 10|qq=}}) – {{ill|Itaya Hazan|ja|板谷波山|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itaya Hazan|qq=}}, a ceramic artist (died [[1963]]).
== Deaths == * [[Tenbun]] 20th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1551]] {{ill|April 8|ja|4月8日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 8|qq=}}) – {{ill|Oda Nobuhide|ja|織田信秀|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobuhide|qq=}}, a military commander and father of Oda Nobunaga (born [[1510]]). * [[Keichō]] 4th year (leap March) ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1599]] {{ill|April 27|ja|4月27日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 27|qq=}}) – {{ill|Maeda Toshiie|ja|前田利家|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maeda Toshiie|qq=}}, a military commander and one of the Tairō; he was the first lord of the Kaga Domain (born [[1538]]). * 安政7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1860, {{ill|March 24|ja|3月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 24|qq=}}) – {{ill|Ii Naosuke|ja|井伊直弼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ii Naosuke|qq=}}, Tairō of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1815]]). * 慶応4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1868, {{ill|March 26|ja|3月26日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 26|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sagara Sōzō|ja|相楽総三|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sagara Sōzō|qq=}}, a Sonnō jōi activist (born [[1839]]).
== Commemorations == * {{ill|Shōmiji|ja|上巳|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōmiji|qq=}} and {{ill|Hina Matsuri|ja|雛祭り|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hina Matsuri|qq=}} * {{ill|Hama-ori|ja|浜下り|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hama-ori|qq=}} – In Okinawa, women purify themselves by presenting food in tiered boxes at the beach; this tradition is combined with clam digging. * 玄天上帝誕辰 – The birthday celebration of the Taoist deity {{ill|Xuantian Shangdi|ja|玄天上帝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xuantian Shangdi|qq=}}. * A traditional event of the Zhuang people in China (in Zhuang language: samnyiedcosam) to honor their ancestors, accompanied by large-scale singing gatherings. * An independent New Year celebration by the Khor Lao ethnic group in Vietnam.
